      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_6971022063746367488.png",
                "key": "如水从平",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "如水从平"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">源水之滴</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/1b23c5ffce1624b3fd3458b534a7f012_6511867287748970998.png",
                "key": "泪水啊，我必偿还",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "泪水啊，我必偿还"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>，对所有后台敌人造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>，生成可用次数为2的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">源水之滴</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/83afd6c7a216ef571b8f3868ecdf5b92_8089478324408229280.png",
                "key": "潮水啊，我已归来",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "潮水啊，我已归来"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害<span>+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成使下次火/雷伤害+2的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span><span>]</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span>我方对敌方出战角色造成</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>时，伤害值<span>+2。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: white\">可用次数：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_9202787585826489238.png",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能</span></strong><br>有些技能无法被直接使用，而是需要一定次数的行动轮来进行<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>。</p><p>轮到一位牌手行动时，如果该牌手的「出战角色」正在<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能，则跳过该牌手的行动：如果技能已经完成<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>，角色将会在此时直接使用此技能。（此类需要<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>的技能，无法触发「使用技能后」效果。）</p><p>只有「出战角色」才能<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能的「出战角色」被切换到后台，技能的<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>就会被打断。<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">衡平推裁<br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击<br></span>（需准备1个行动轮）<br>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，如果生命值至少为6，则对自身造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span>，使伤害+1。<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数<br></span></strong>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害<br></span></strong>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">源水之滴<br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">那维莱特进行普通攻击后：</span>治疗角色2点，然后角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能：衡平推裁</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到3次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1874651882339029620.png",
